 10. The main reason for this update was to get the plugin working better with W3 Total Cache where counts weren&#8217;t updated due to its aggressive caching. The [&#8230;]<hr style=\"border-top:black solid 1px\" /><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/06/16/top-10-v1-9-6/\">Top 10 v1.9.6</a> was first posted on June 16, 2013 at 10:46 am.<br />© 2003-2013 \"<a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com\">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>\". All rights reserved.<br />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Ajay D\\&#039;Souza\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2023:\"<div class=\"KonaBody\"><p><strong>Update: v1.9.6 still has bugs on some installs where the Ajax is not run and counts are not incremented.</strong></p>\n<p>I pushed through relatively minor updates to Top 10. The main reason for this update was to get the plugin working better with W3 Total Cache where counts weren&#8217;t updated due to its aggressive caching.</p>\n<p>The title of the posts also have their very own title tag which allows you to separately style this. And, lastly, users can now turn on or off the counting for overall and / or daily posts. So, if you don&#8217;t need the daily counter, you&#8217;ll get some performance improvements. v1.9.6 fixes bugs introduced in v1.9.5 where the daily counter remained off permanently.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3521\" alt=\"Top 10 v1.9.6\" src=\"http://i0.wp.com/ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Top-10-v1.9.6.png?resize=496%2C180\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>As usual, if you&#8217;re seeking support on the plugin check out the <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/top-10\">support forum</a> first. And, if you&#8217;ve been using this plugin a lot, do consider giving a <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/top-10\">5 star review</a>.</p>\n<h3>Changes in 1.9.5 and 1.9.6</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>New: CSS class <code>tptn_title</code> that can be used to style the title of the posts</li>\n<li>New: Option to disable Daily or Overall counters</li>\n<li>Fixed: Counter to work with different directory structures. <em>Thanks Nathan for the fix</em></li>\n<li>Fixed: To make it work with W3 Total Cache. <em>Thanks Angelo for the fix</em></li>\n<li>Modified: timthumb will now work if you have JetPack Proton activated</li>\n</ul>\n</div><hr style=\"border-top:black solid 1px\" /><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/06/16/top-10-v1-9-6/\">Top 10 v1.9.6</a> was first posted on June 16, 2013 at 10:46 am.<br />© 2003-2013 \"<a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com\">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>\". All rights reserved.<br />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/06/16/top-10-v1-9-6/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Contextual Related Posts v1.8.8\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4: